name: Prambanan Temple
description: One of the photo collections that was produced from my cellphone, when I was playing in the Yogyakarta, East Java, Indonesia area I have written a list of what I must visit and take photos, and this is the photo I like the most out of all the photos I took at the time. that, the splendor of the Prambanan temple plus the beauty of the super majestic evening sky
